This software is an independent Python/USB port that follows the serial protocol
of the Arduino library "ResenseHEX"
(https://github.com/TUDA-MUST/ResenseHEX, MIT License, (c) Mark Suppelt /
TU Darmstadt). It targets desktop and single-board-computer operating systems
over USB CDC-ACM instead of an Arduino UART.

This is an unofficial project and is not affiliated with, authorized, or
endorsed by Resense. "Resense" and "HEX" are trademarks of their respective
owner.
